sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe / Istio<br/>(TLS termination + Auth)
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant MW as InferenceMiddleware<br/>(CloudEvents)
    participant Batch as Adaptive Batcher<br/>(size/time queue)
    participant Cache as Response Cache<br/>(FIFO)
    participant Pool as Parallel Inference Pool<br/>(multiprocessing.Queue)
    participant Model as MLModel.predict()<br/>(Runtime Plugin)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>/mnt/models
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Client, Model: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>KServe: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>(HTTPS, Bearer Token)
    KServe->>REST: Forward request<br/>(HTTP 8080, TLS terminated)
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlane handler
    DP->>MW: Apply InferenceMiddleware
    MW->>Cache: Check response cache
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>MW: Cached response
        MW-->>DP: Return cached
    else Cache Miss
        MW->>Batch: Queue for batching
        Batch->>Model: Batched predict()
        Model-->>Batch: Batched response
        Batch-->>MW: Split individual responses
        MW->>Cache: Store in cache
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>KServe: HTTP 200 JSON
    KServe-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client, Model: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>KServe: ModelInfer RPC<br/>(gRPC, TLS)
    KServe->>gRPC: Forward request<br/>(gRPC 8081, insecure)
    gRPC->>DP: Route to DataPlane
    DP->>Model: predict()
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP-->>gRPC: gRPC response
    gRPC-->>KServe: ModelInferResponse
    KServe-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Kafka, Model: Flow 3: Kafka Event-Driven Inference
    Kafka->>Kafka: Consumer reads from input topic<br/>(9092/TCP)
    Note right of Kafka: MLServer Kafka Consumer
    Kafka->>DP: Kafka handler → DataPlane
    DP->>Model: predict()
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP->>Kafka: Producer writes to output topic<br/>(9092/TCP)

    Note over DP, Pool: Flow 4: Parallel Inference
    DP->>Pool: Dispatch to worker<br/>(round-robin)
    Pool->>Model: Worker process predict()<br/>(IPC Queue)
    Model-->>Pool: Response via Queue
    Pool-->>DP: Merged response

    Note over Model, Storage: Model Loading
    Storage-->>Model: Load model artifacts<br/>(/mnt/models filesystem)

    Note over REST, OTel: Observability
    REST->>OTel: Export traces<br/>(OTLP gRPC 4317, insecure)
    gRPC->>OTel: Export traces<br/>(OTLP gRPC 4317, insecure)
    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape /metrics<br/>(HTTP 8082)
